<plot>A teacher from the Ministry of Education is on his way to bring study books for the children in a remote mountain village, North of Iran. But he is stopped in the snow by a pack of hungry wolves. A boy in the village, busy reading the book "The last village", tries to convince the people of the village to rescue the teacher.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?027638</url></doc>
